dct_title_s: Middle East briefing map. Series 1308 [cartographic material].
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Shows area from Isparta in the northwest and Qena in the southwest to Ayn Zalah in the northeast and Tabah in the southeast including international boundaries, armistice lines, cities, primary and secondary roads, railroads, airfields, rivers and lakes. "11-73."
dct_creator_sm: United States. Defense Mapping Agency. Topographic Center
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D.C.] : Defense Mapping Agency, Topographic Center, [1973].
